OL,3,CMan charged with murder after
OL,4,Cshopkeeper stabbed to death
OL,6,FA man has been charged with the murder
OL,7,Fof a mother was stabbed to death in
OL,8,Fthe shop where she worked.
OL,10,FNilani Nimalarajah was found seriously
OL,11,Finjured at Low Cost Food and Wine on
OL,12,FStanley Road in Bootle on Friday, 20
OL,13,FJune.
OL,15,FThe 44-year-old was taken to hospital
OL,16,Fin a critical condition but she died a
OL,17,Fshort time later. A Home Office post-
OL,18,Fmortem found she died as a result of
OL,19,Fstab wounds to her chest.
