OL,3,CMan charged with murder after
OL,4,Cshopkeeper stabbed to death
OL,6,FMerseyside Police have now charged
OL,7,FNimalarajah Mathiyadaranam, 47, with
OL,8,Fmurder and possession of a knife blade/
OL,9,Fsharp pointed article in a public
OL,10,Fplace and two breaches of restraining
OL,11,Forders.
OL,13,FThe force say Mathiyadaranam had been
OL,14,Ftreated in hospital following the
OL,15,Fincident, but was discharged on
OL,16,FWednesday, 16 July.
