OL,4,Cshopkeeper stabbed to death
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Alan Nuttall
OL,7,Furged people not to share material
OL,8,Frelated to the incident online and
OL,9,Fsaid the force continued to appeal for
OL,10,Fanyone with information to come
OL,11,Fforward.
OL,13,FDetective Chief Inspector Alan Nuttall
OL,14,Fsaid: "A man has now been charged so I
OL,15,Fwould like to take this opportunity to
OL,16,Fremind people that this is a live
OL,17,Finvestigation, and to be mindful that
OL,18,Fanything posted or shared on social
OL,19,Fmedia could jeopardise proceedings, so
OL,20,Fplease support us as we move forward
OL,21,Fwith the case.
