OL,6,F"The best way to help is to pass
OL,7,Finformation on through official
OL,8,Fchannels. To that end, we are still
OL,9,Fkeen to hear from anyone who may hold
OL,10,Finformation and not yet made
OL,11,Fthemselves known to police."
OL,13,FLocal resident Constantin Manzu said
OL,14,FMs Nimalarajah was "known by many in
OL,15,Fthe community." He said: "Every time
OL,16,Fwe went to the shop she was always
OL,17,Fchatting with every single person in
OL,18,Fthe shop.
