OL,6,F"It wasn't just the people who would
OL,7,Fgo in the shop, it was even the people
OL,8,Fin the street. She would come out and
OL,9,Fspeak to people.
OL,11,F"She would always be out with the kids
OL,12,Ftoo, taking the kids to school,
OL,13,Fpicking them up, and looking after the
OL,14,Fshop as well."
